ActCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
SubjectCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation (CDIC) ** Maximum annual premium **
PrecisOrder fixing at two ninths of one per cent the percentage used for the purpose of assessing the MAXIMUM ANNUAL PREMIUM of each member institution for the premium year beginning on May 1, 2011 and ending on April 30, 2012.
